replies.body:
It's a amazing how easily people can miss the obvious (;

You could have slimmed this down and avoided the double passive, by simply having him gather the meeps instead of chimes.

But I guess you had the chimes first and added the meeps later?

Yeah prepare for the raging adc's "NO SUPPORT GG" and yes the ult is definitely going to get some people chewed out lol. 

However he does look really fun and honestly he seems like a strong support to have without roaming to other lanes. Time will tell but I'm definitely gonna pick him up when he comes out

Oh and the tower dive potential is strong in this one. {{item:3070}}  {{item:3056}}
